text = "\"on_activated\" signal is emitted 
once the \"Weight To Activate\" is reached.
\"on_deactivated\" is emitted when
the current weight is 0.
\"on_change\" is emitted any time 
an item or entity enter/leaves the plate,
The signal value is 
current_weight/weight_to_activate"
font_size = 17
autowrap_mode = 1

